<bibRefCitation author="Van Soest, RWM" journalOrPublisher="Contributions to Zoology" pageId="52" pageNumber="53" pagination="121 - 142" title="Sponge diversity and community composition in Irish bathyal coral reefs." volume="76" year="2007">van Soest et al. 2007</bibRefCitation>
